    "title": "Noa",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "noa",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Noa alikuwa mwana wa Lameki na mzao wa Sethi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:3-Gen5:29\">Mwanzo 5:3–29</a>). Lameki alitarajia kwamba Noa, ambaye jina lake linamaanisha &quot;pumziko&quot; au &quot;faraja,&quot; angepunguza laana ya kazi ngumu kwenye ardhi. Hata hivyo, Mungu alimtumia Noa kusaidia kuondoa uovu duniani.</p><p>Mungu alipanga kuangamiza uumbaji kwa sababu ya uovu wa binadamu uliokuwa umeenea (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:1-Gen6:7\">Mwanzo 6:1–7</a>; angalia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:37-Matt24:39\">Mathayo 24:37–39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:26-Luke17:27\">Luka 17:26–27</a>), lakini aliamua kumwokoa Noa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:8\">Mwanzo 6:8</a>). Mungu alimpa Noa, ambaye alikuwa mwenye haki na asiye na lawama (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9\">Mwanzo 6:9</a>), maagizo ya kina ya kujenga safina. Ni familia ya Noa ya watu wanane na kila aina ya kiumbe tu ndio wangeokolewa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:14-Gen8:19\">Mwanzo 6:14–8:19</a>). Baada ya Gharika, Noa na familia yake walitoka kwenye safina. Noa alimfurahisha Mungu kwa kujenga madhabahu na kutoa dhabihu. Mungu aliahidi kamwe kutogharikisha dunia nzima tena au kuvuruga misimu, licha ya dhambi za binadamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20-Gen9:17\">Mwanzo 8:20–9:17</a>).</p><p>Wana wa Noa walikuwa Shemu, Hamu, na Yafethi. Mataifa yote ya dunia yalitokana nao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:18-Gen9:19\">Mwanzo 9:18–19</a>). Wakati Noa alipolewa kwa divai aliyotengeneza, wanawe na kizazi chao walilaaniwa au kubarikiwa kulingana na matendo yao kwake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:20-Gen9:27\">Mwanzo 9:20–27</a>). Noa aliishi kwa miaka 950, ikiwa ni pamoja na miaka 350 baada ya Gharika (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:28-Gen9:29\">Mwanzo 9:28–29</a>). Yeye ni mfano wa uadilifu, utii, ujasiri, na imani (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:12-Ezek14:20\">Ezekieli 14:12–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:7\">Waebrania 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:5\">2 Petro 2:5</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:28-Gen10:1\">Mwanzo 5:28–10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr1:4\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:9\">Isaya 54:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:12-Ezek14:20\">Ezekieli 14:12–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:37-Matt24:38\">Mathayo 24:37–38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:36\">Luka 3:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:26-Luke17:27\">Luka 17:26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:7\">Waebrania 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:20-1Pet3:21\">1 Petro 3:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:5\">2 Petro 2:5</a></p>",
